data.description: ABSOLUTELY STUNNING!!! This amazing open concept home is waiting for the new owner. Walk in through the beautiful foyer into the INCREDIBLE open concept great room/kitchen/dining area. The great room features gorgeous flooring, tons of natural light and gas fireplace. Kitchen has gorgeous grey subway tile, tons and tons of cabinets, double sink and so much counter space! Dining area features doorwall to back yard.  The primary bedroom has so much space, walk in closet and full bath with beautiful stand up shower. The other bedrooms are a good size with large closets. Basement is unfinished with plenty of potential. Whole house generator provides full power during a power outage.  Outside you will find a beautiful spacious yard with concrete patio. Seller is relocating for their job - this means an opportunity for you!! Do not miss this one!! BATVD
